# Experiment INDEX

List of experiment notebooks with one-line conclusions. `scripts/new_experiment.py` adds
new entries automatically.

## Entries

| exp_id | Purpose | Linked hypothesis | Status | Conclusion (one line) |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| exp_001 | (example) Define data universe | (foundation) | done | ... |
| exp_002 | (example) Factor IC screening | H1 | done | ... |
| exp_003 | ... | ... | in-progress | ... |

## Status legend

- `planned`: entry exists in hypotheses.md, notebook not created
- `in-progress`: notebook created, conclusion not yet finalized
- `done`: conclusion cell filled and result row appended
- `parked`: blocked on upstream dependency
- `dropped`: judged not worth pursuing; reason recorded in decisions.md

## Order

Sequential numbering, but dependencies (upstream first) take precedence. Each notebook
states its upstream dependencies in its "Upstream dependencies" section.
